## Summary
This documentation page describes the Intercom (Cohort Sync) destination integration in Amplitude, which allows sending behavioral cohorts from Amplitude to Intercom for targeted user engagement based on product interactions and lifecycle timing, supporting real-time sync that updates each minute.

